OL,3,CNew 'minimum standards' regulations
OL,4,Cfor landlords
OL,6,FLandlords in Guernsey could face fines
OL,7,Fand lose their ability to rent out
OL,8,Fproperties if they do not comply with
OL,9,Fnew minimum property standards set by
OL,10,Fthe States.
OL,12,FPoliticians voted in favour of
OL,13,Fintroducing the legislation, which
OL,14,Fincludes seven new 'minimum standards'
OL,15,Fto ensure excess mould is cleared,
OL,16,Fthere is proper ventilation and rooms
OL,17,Fare not overcrowded.
