OL,3,CNew 'minimum standards' regulations
OL,4,Cfor landlords
OL,6,FDeputy Lyndsay De Sausmarez, the
OL,7,Fcommittee's President says: "Until
OL,8,Fnow, I've had to explain to people who
OL,9,Fhave sent me the most awful photos and
OL,10,Ftales of their own experiences of what
OL,11,Fit's like to live in such properties -
OL,12,FI've had to say 'I'm really sorry but
OL,13,Fthere is very little anyone can do
OL,14,Funtil we get this legislation in
OL,15,Fplace'. So I'm really glad that this
OL,16,Flegislation is a real, definitive step
OL,17,Falong that process.
